OL,3,CBordeaux flights could bring more
OL,4,CFrench tourists to Jersey, says Ports
OL,6,FDirect flights between Jersey and
OL,7,FBordeaux could attract more French
OL,8,Fvisitors to the island, according to
OL,9,Fthe head of the island's Ports.
OL,11,FMatt Thomas's comments follow
OL,12,FLoganair's announcement that it will
OL,13,Fbe running twice-weekly seasonal
OL,14,Fservices to the city on Mondays and
OL,15,FFridays from 19 June to 5 October.
OL,17,FOne-way fares will start at #79.99
OL,18,Ffrom Jersey and E89.99 from Bordeaux.
OL,26,@zD@QOk
