OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776607869
OL,3,CBordeaux flights could bring more
OL,4,CFrench tourists to Jersey, says Ports
OL,6,FMr Thomas adds: "This represents a
OL,7,Fvaluable opportunity for both inbound
OL,8,Ftourism and outbound travel.
OL,10,F"We're pleased to continue working
OL,11,Fclosely with Loganair as they further
OL,12,Fbuild their presence and long-term
OL,13,Finvestment in Jersey.
OL,15,F"The introduction of direct flights to
OL,16,FBordeaux marks an exciting step
OL,17,Fforward for Jersey's European
OL,18,Fconnectivity."
