OL,3,CBordeaux flights could bring more
OL,4,CFrench tourists to Jersey, says Ports
OL,6,FLoganair took over many of Jersey's
OL,7,Fair services after the collapse of
OL,8,FBlue Islands in November.
OL,10,FAlongside several UK routes, they have
OL,11,Fsince expanded to cover Paris Charles
OL,12,Fde Gaulle and Dublin.
OL,14,FRonnie Matheson, the airline's Chief
OL,15,FCommercial Officer, explains: "We
OL,16,Fremain committed to enhancing
OL,17,Fconnectivity for Jersey, and this
OL,18,Flatest addition, alongside our wider
OL,19,Fnetwork of seasonal services, ensures
OL,20,Fcustomers have even greater choice
OL,21,Fwhen planning their summer travel."
