OL,3,CBordeaux flights could bring more
OL,4,CFrench tourists to Jersey, says Ports
OL,6,FSimon Dreschel, Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer at Bordeaux Airport, adds:
OL,8,F"The launch of this route to Jersey
OL,9,Fand the arrival of a new airline on
OL,10,Four tarmac enriches the diversity of
OL,11,Four network with a destination that is
OL,12,Fboth unique and refreshingly
OL,13,Fdifferent."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
